        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[#一周不洗脸为什么皮肤变好了#[吃惊] 一周不洗脸皮肤会不会变好小卫不知道，但一定会脏[允悲]皮脂腺分泌的油脂是我们皮肤的一道天然保护膜，它能滋润皮肤，还有...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%97%E8%84%B8%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%8F%98%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%86%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E4%B8%8D%E6%B4%97%E8%84%B8%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E7%9A%AE%E8%82%A4%E5%8F%98%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%86%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#一周不洗脸为什么皮肤变好了#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span> 一周不洗脸皮肤会不会变好小卫不知道，但一定会脏<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[允悲]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_yunbei-a14a649db8.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><br><br>皮脂腺分泌的油脂是我们皮肤的一道天然保护膜，它能滋润皮肤，还有一定的抗菌作用。但是，超过两天不洗脸，油脂、灰尘、细菌等在脸上大量堆积会堵塞毛孔容易感染，可能引发皮炎、痤疮等问题。<br><br>脸部适度清洁还是很重要的，小卫建议，每日可早晚洁面两次。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%9D%A5%E8%BE%9F%E8%B0%A3%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫来辟谣#</span></a>（新华社、健康中国）<img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hkhnc1xfqgj20m808ct8x.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
